{
  "stem": "2723.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I found him in the second part of the flat, which was another room, bitterly crying.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that was a very significant moment to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was really, truly horrified what I had to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was I who had to reassure him that I was all right.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He carried my suitcase, but only to the bottom of the stairs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He wasn't allowed to, and that upset him very much too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we came back, and I feel extremely lucky.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We suddenly had a change of underwear and all the rest of it, and we felt equal to the others and started the journey.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we came to Sered which, ironically, was my father's birth place, I really hoped we would meet people and see people, and-- nobody.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were all strange places.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My fervent hope that I would see Mother there was obviously not realized.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She had been taken away already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Still, we had no idea what was ahead of us because this was no longer peopled, or guarded, by Germans.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were fully overseen by the Slovak part of the collaborators.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were far worse.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they kept feeding us the idea that we were going to work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I guess I was perhaps smarter than-- than I knew, because I thought, what sort of work can we do, my sister and I?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I asked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was smart ass, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he responded and said, you look strong enough, and your sister will go to school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I bought it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How long we were in Sered, I don't remember, but I do know that we were fed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had some kind of accommodation, and-- and found a number of acquaintances, and that made it a bit more bearable.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
